<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id605558d8-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s1501"><num value="1501">§ 1501.</num><heading> Congressional statement of findings</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Congress finds that—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id605558d9-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s1501/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> domestic geothermal reserves can be developed into regionally significant energy sources promoting the economic health and national security of the Nation;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id605558da-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s1501/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> there are institutional and economic barriers to the commercialization of geothermal technology; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id605558db-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s1501/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> Federal agencies should consider the use of geothermal energy in the Government’s buildings.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id605558dc-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/294/tVI/s602">Pub. L. 96–294, title VI, § 602</ref>, <date date="1980-06-30">June 30, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/763">94 Stat. 763</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id605558dd-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id605558de-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="shortTitle" id="id605558df-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Short Title</heading><p><ref href="/us/pl/96/294/tVI/s601">Pub. L. 96–294, title VI, § 601</ref>, <date date="1980-06-30">June 30, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/763">94 Stat. 763</ref>, provided that: <quotedContent origin="/us/pl/96/294/tVI/s601">“This title [enacting this chapter and sections 1146 and 1147 of this title and amending sections 1141 and 1143 of this title and sections 796, 824a–3, 824i, and 824j of Title 16, Conservation] may be cited as the ‘Geothermal Energy Act of 1980’.”</quotedContent>
</p>
</note>
</notes>
